org.apache.polygene.spi.entitystore.helpers

Class MapEntityStoreMixin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.polygene.spi.entitystore.helpers.MapEntityStoreMixin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityStore, EntityStoreSPI, MapEntityStoreActivation, StateStore

    public class MapEntityStoreMixin
extends Object
implements EntityStore, EntityStoreSPI, StateStore, MapEntityStoreActivation
    Implementation of EntityStore that works with an implementation of MapEntityStore.

    Implement MapEntityStore and add as mixin to the service using this mixin.

    See MemoryMapEntityStoreMixin for reference.

    EntityStores based on this mixin gets support for the Migration extension.

    MapEntityStore implementations will get their values as JSON.
